You are implementing Tasks 1-4 of the OpenAI Responses API migration plan.

## Task Description

You need to make these changes to the OpenAI adapter in `internal/agent/openai/`:

### Task 1: Add config fields to WebSearch

Modify `internal/agent/openai/websearch.go`:
