2. `convertResponseTools(req *model.LLMRequest, wsConfig *WebSearch) []responseTool` ŌĆö converts ADK tools to Responses API flat format. Function tools become `{type: "function", name, description, parameters}` (flat, NOT nested in a `function` key). If GoogleSearch marker is present, adds `{type: "web_search", search_context_size, filters}` using wsConfig.

3. `convertResponseOutput(resp *responsesResponse) *model.LLMResponse` ŌĆö converts Responses API output items to ADK LLMResponse. Maps `function_call` items to `genai.FunctionCall` parts (use `call_id` as the ID). Maps `message` items' text content to text parts. Skips `web_search_call` items. Sets usage metadata.

